Description: Handle of Knidian pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp
Type series: KT1002 (in Grace's unpublished K(nidian) T(ype) series)
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p. 27a, 25. Names, Euphranor, Menes. From same die as Athenian Agora SS181.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0320)
